FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]
WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]

    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]
WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

END = CAST(1 AS bit)"

""SELECT [p].[PermissionListId], [p].[ActionName], [p].[Area], [p].[ControllerName], [p].[Descript], [p].[ParentId], [p].[Radif], [p].[Status]
FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]
WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

    WHEN [p].[Status] = 0 AND [p].[Status] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END = CAST(1 AS bit)"

    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

""SELECT [p].[PermissionListId], [p].[ActionName], [p].[Area], [p].[ControllerName], [p].[Descript], [p].[ParentId], [p].[Radif], [p].[Status]
FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]
WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END & CASE
    WHEN [p].[Status] = 0 AND [p].[Status] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END = CAST(1 AS bit)"

FROM [dbo].[PermissionList] AS [p]
WHERE CASE
    WHEN [p].[ParentId] = 0 AND [p].[ParentId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
